org.apache.chemistry.opencmis.commons.server

Interface RenditionInfo

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RenditionInfoImpl

    public interface RenditionInfo
    Contains information about a rendition of an object. This data is used to generate the appropriate links in AtomPub entries and feeds.
